  "title": "Part Time In-House Livestream Sales Host",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role Overview</strong></p><p><u>This is a sales-focused livestream host role, not an influencer or posting position.</u></p><p>You will host TikTok Shop livestreams on Goldlion’s official account, selling men’s fashion products and driving live sales.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Livestream Hosting & Sales</li><li>Host TikTok Shop livestreams on Goldlion’s official account</li><li>Promote and sell men’s fashion during live sessions</li><li>Livestream in Goldlion office (Mon–Fri, 9am–6pm; flexible scheduling within office hours)</li><li>Use your own style and creative selling approach during livestreams</li><li>Engage viewers, answer questions, and close sales live</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Comfortable speaking on camera and selling live</li><li>Clear, confident communication and on-screen presence</li><li>Coachable and open to feedback</li><li>Reliable availability for scheduled livestream hours</li></ul><p><u><strong>Experience</strong></u></p><ul><li>Livestream selling or retail sales experience is a plus</li></ul><p><u><strong>What This Role Is (and Is Not)</strong></u></p><p><u>This Role Is:</u><br />✔ Brand-owned livestream sales position<br />✔ Opportunity to build recognition as a recurring host<br />✔ Performance-based earnings tied to sales<br />✔ Must work on-site at Goldlion Office</p><p><u>This Role Is NOT:</u><br />✖ Not an influencer or KOL role<br />✖ No posting on personal social media accounts<br />✖ No ownership of livestream account or data<br />✖ NOT remote / work-from-home</p><p><u><strong>Compensation & Benefits</strong></u></p><ul><li>Hourly base pay for livestream sessions</li><li>Sales commission based on livestream performance</li><li>Paid trial period provided</li><li>Long-term collaboration and higher earning potential based on results</li></ul><p>📩<strong>How to Apply:</strong><br />APPLY HERE or Submit your resume/CV to: <em><strong>hr@goldlion.com.sg</strong></em></p>",
