    "description": "<p>GOLDLION ENTERPRISE (SINGAPORE) PTE LTD</p>\n<p>GOLDLION’s fine merchandise are crafted with the urban man &amp; woman in mind. This is matched with a balance of technology and workmanship.&nbsp; Since 1968, GOLDLION has delivered high quality and innovative technology of Apparel, Accessories, Leather goods and Ties.&nbsp; The brand now has 1,090 stores worldwide.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our Mission<br>\nTo be the preferred formalwear brand for contemporary men.<br>\n<br>\nOur Vision<br>\nTo provide high quality and tasteful lifestyle for contemporary men.<br>\n<br>\nOur Values<br>\nPatriotism, Diligence &amp; Honesty, Premium Quality.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
